quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,84,"Maaku: \"Men gom…óinii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba e Taaniraa…ďe …ďen e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e Annabaa…ďe …ďen immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Men serndataa hakkunde gooto e ma…ď…ďe, Menen wonannde Mo ko men jebbilii…ďe"
  3,85,"Kala …óa…ď…ďu…óo ko woori Lislaamu on Diina, o ja…ďaŇčtaake …óum, on …óon ka laakara, ko o jeyaa…óo e hayru…ďe …ďen"
  3,86,"Hol no Alla Fewnirta yim…ďe yeddu…ďe …ďaawo gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe …ďe seedii wonnde Nulaa…óo on ko goonga, …ďanngannduyeeji …óin arii …ďe? Alla Fewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,87,"∆Āen …óon, jo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, ko no fawii …ďe kuddi Alla ndin e Malaa'ika en e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe denndaangal"
  3,88,"Ko …ďe luttoo…ďe e magge. ∆Āe hayfinaŇčtaake lepte …óen, …ďe wonaali nennanaŇčtee…ďe"
  3,89,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďaawo …óum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini. Pellet, Alla ko Yaafotoo…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  3,90,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďaawo gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe, refti …ďe …ďeydorii keeferaaku, tuubugol ma…ď…ďe ja…ďetaake; ko …ďen …óon woni majju…ďe …ďen"
  3,91,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayi ko …ďe heerer…ďe, gooto e ma…ď…ďe ja…ďaŇčtaake, leydi ndin tew kaŇčŇče; hay si o soktorii …óum. ∆Āen …óon, no woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe, …ďe alaa walloo…ďe"
